org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface BoolLEDComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoolLEDComponentImpl

    public interface BoolLEDComponent
extends Component
    A representation of the model object 'Bool LED Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Format
    • Descriptor
    • Alarm
    • Attribute
    • Expected Value
    • On Off

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getBoolLEDComponent()
